## Guardrails

**In analysis slot**: Read files, explore codebase, create plans, dispatch work. NEVER create/modify source files or run state-mutating commands.

**If user provides inline plan**: Save to `memory/plans/`, {{#IF_PLAN_DISPATCH}}dispatch via ticket{{/IF_PLAN_DISPATCH}}. NEVER implement directly.
